; What would the interpreter print in response to evaluating each of the 
; following expressions?

(define (memq item x) 
    (cond ((null? x) false)
          ((eq? item (car x)) x) 
          (else (memq item (cdr x)))))

(list 'a 'b 'c)
; (a b c)

(list (list 'george))
; ((george))

(cdr '((x1 x2) (y1 y2)))
; ((y1 y2))

(cadr '((x1 x2) (y1 y2)))
; (y1 y2)

(pair? (car '(a short list)))
; #f

(memq 'red '((red shoes) (blue socks)))
; #f

(memq 'red '(red shoes blue socks))
; (red shoes blue socks)
